                <mxCell id="cellnote" value="Scout lifecycle: receive → verify (auth key) → execute role → detect trigger → { task | communicate | clone | terminate }   •   Self-forming &amp; self-terminating cells   •   ISLAND MODE: runs hours/days with no WAN   •   Self-forming federations under a scout-master   •   clone / transfer-authority to scale &amp; heal" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f5f5f5;strokeColor=#666666;align=left;spacingLeft=10;fontColor=#333333;" parent="cells" vertex="1">
