                <mxCell id="xle" value="Learning Engine — the spine&#xa;retrieval &amp; adaptation from history:&#xa;ranks CAPs • matches CaCSM patterns&#xa;• matches DNA schemas • picks POV&#xa;patterns • recalibrates states live" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#d5e8d4;strokeColor=#82b366;align=left;spacingLeft=8;verticalAlign=top;spacingTop=6;" parent="xcut" vertex="1">
